  "texts": [
    "The specific LLMs employed for this zero-shot learning task are detailed in Table 3.2 Fine-TuningThis study investigates the impact of different training methodologies on the accuracy of sentiment analysis adapted to the domain of oil market news.",
    "We employ a hierarchical classification approach to analyze sentiment concerning four key events related to the OM dataset.",
    "The first level classification is the binary classification model that is fine-tuned on the subset of OM dataset.",
    "Contingent upon the article being classified as \"Relevant,\" the second level of the hierarchy is trained without using the 200 \"Not Relevant\" sentences, ensuring that the models are trained solely on data pertinent to the oil commodity domain.",
    "Furthermore, the labeling strategy for each of these second-level classifiers is refined to enhance specificity."
  ]
}